  "description": "This game attempts to conduct a simplified abstract analysis of the capitalist society by simulating the transactions, circulation and transformation of elements such as surplus value, commodities, debts, equities, and land rights in the market.\n\nEach economic unit in the game will act autonomously based on its own role. Detailed information can be viewed in its role panel. Players can freely choose any economic unit as their control object to experience economic games from different perspectives.\n\nThe game is still in the improvement stage and may have errors or omissions. If any are found, please kindly correct them.",
  "description_short": "This game is an abstract simulation of capitalism through the trade, flow, and conversion of surplus value, commodities, debt, equity, and land rights. Each unit has unique behaviors and an asset panel updated in real time.",
